                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300916-74-off387 t18300916-74-cd388"></join>, 1 silk handkerchief, value 3s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18300916-74-victim718" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
